{
    "poem_title": "Le Danube en colère",
    "author": "Victor Hugo",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1829",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Belgrade et Semlin sont en guerre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Dans son lit, paisible naguère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Le vieillard Danube leur père",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "S'éveille au bruit de leur canon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Il doute s'il rêve, il tressaille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Puis entend gronder la bataille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et frappe dans ses mains d'écaille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et les appelle par leur nom.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Belgrade et Semlin sont en guerre.\nDans son lit, paisible naguère,\nLe vieillard Danube leur père\nS'éveille au bruit de leur canon.\nIl doute s'il rêve, il tressaille,\nPuis entend gronder la bataille,\nEt frappe dans ses mains d'écaille,\nEt les appelle par leur nom."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "\" Allons ! la turque et la chrétienne !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Semlin ! Belgrade ! qu'avez-vous ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "On ne peut, le ciel me soutienne !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Dormir un siècle, sans que vienne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Vous éveiller d'un bruit jaloux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Belgrade ou Semlin en courroux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Allons ! la turque et la chrétienne !\nSemlin ! Belgrade ! qu'avez-vous ?\nOn ne peut, le ciel me soutienne !\nDormir un siècle, sans que vienne\nVous éveiller d'un bruit jaloux\nBelgrade ou Semlin en courroux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "\" Hiver, été, printemps, automne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Toujours votre canon qui tonne !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Bercé du courant monotone,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Je sommeillais dans mes roseaux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Et, comme des louves marines",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Jettent l'onde de leurs narines,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Voilà vos longues couleuvrines",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Qui soufflent du feu sur mes eaux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Hiver, été, printemps, automne,\nToujours votre canon qui tonne !\nBercé du courant monotone,\nJe sommeillais dans mes roseaux ;\nEt, comme des louves marines\nJettent l'onde de leurs narines,\nVoilà vos longues couleuvrines\nQui soufflent du feu sur mes eaux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "\" Ce sont des sorcières oisives",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Qui vous mirent, pour rire un jour,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Face à face sur mes deux rives,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Comme au même plat deux convives,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Comme au front de la même tour",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Une aire d'aigle, un nid d'autour.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Ce sont des sorcières oisives\nQui vous mirent, pour rire un jour,\nFace à face sur mes deux rives,\nComme au même plat deux convives,\nComme au front de la même tour\nUne aire d'aigle, un nid d'autour."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "\" Quoi ! ne pouvez-vous vivre ensemble,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Mes filles ? faut-il que je tremble",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Du destin qui ne vous rassemble",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Que pour vous haïr de plus près,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Quand vous pourriez, surs pacifiques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Mirer dans mes eaux magnifiques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Semlin, tes noirs clochers gothiques,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Belgrade, tes blancs minarets !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Quoi ! ne pouvez-vous vivre ensemble,\nMes filles ? faut-il que je tremble\nDu destin qui ne vous rassemble\nQue pour vous haïr de plus près,\nQuand vous pourriez, surs pacifiques,\nMirer dans mes eaux magnifiques,\nSemlin, tes noirs clochers gothiques,\nBelgrade, tes blancs minarets !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "\" Mon flot, qui dans l'océan tombe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Vous sépare en vain, large et clair ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Du haut du château qui surplombe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Vous vous unissez, et la bombe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Entre vous courbant son éclair,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Vous trace un pont de feu dans l'air.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Mon flot, qui dans l'océan tombe,\nVous sépare en vain, large et clair ;\nDu haut du château qui surplombe\nVous vous unissez, et la bombe,\nEntre vous courbant son éclair,\nVous trace un pont de feu dans l'air."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "\" Trêve ! taisez-vous, les deux villes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Je m'ennuie aux guerres civiles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Nous sommes vieux, soyons tranquilles.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Dormons à l'ombre des bouleaux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Trêve à ces débats de familles !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Hé ! sans le bruit de vos bastilles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "N'ai-je donc point assez, mes filles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "De l'assourdissement des flots ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Trêve ! taisez-vous, les deux villes !\nJe m'ennuie aux guerres civiles.\nNous sommes vieux, soyons tranquilles.\nDormons à l'ombre des bouleaux.\nTrêve à ces débats de familles !\nHé ! sans le bruit de vos bastilles,\nN'ai-je donc point assez, mes filles,\nDe l'assourdissement des flots ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "\" Une croix, un croissant fragile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Changent en enfer ce beau lieu ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Vous échangez la bombe agile",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Pour le koran et l'évangile ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "C'est perdre le bruit et le feu :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Je le sais, moi qui fus un dieu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Une croix, un croissant fragile\nChangent en enfer ce beau lieu ?\nVous échangez la bombe agile\nPour le koran et l'évangile ?\nC'est perdre le bruit et le feu :\nJe le sais, moi qui fus un dieu !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "\" Vos dieux m'ont chassé de leur sphère",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Et dégradé, c'est leur affaire !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "L'ombre est le bien que je préfère,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Pourvu qu'ils gardent leurs palais,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Et ne viennent pas sur mes plages",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Déracines mes verts feuillages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "Et m'écraser mes coquillages",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Sous leurs bombes et leurs boulets !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Vos dieux m'ont chassé de leur sphère\nEt dégradé, c'est leur affaire !\nL'ombre est le bien que je préfère,\nPourvu qu'ils gardent leurs palais,\nEt ne viennent pas sur mes plages\nDéracines mes verts feuillages,\nEt m'écraser mes coquillages\nSous leurs bombes et leurs boulets !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "\" De leurs abominables cultes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Ces inventions sont le fruit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "De mon temps point de ces tumultes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Si la pierre des catapultes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Battait les cités jour et nuit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "C'était sans fumée et sans bruit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" De leurs abominables cultes\nCes inventions sont le fruit.\nDe mon temps point de ces tumultes.\nSi la pierre des catapultes\nBattait les cités jour et nuit,\nC'était sans fumée et sans bruit."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "\" Voyez Ulm, votre sur jumelle :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Tenez-vous en repos comme elle.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Que le fil des rois se démêle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Tournez vos fuseaux, et riez.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Voyez Bude, votre voisine ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Voyez Dristra la sarrasine !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Que dirait l'Etna si Messine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Faisait tout ce bruit à ses pieds ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Voyez Ulm, votre sur jumelle :\nTenez-vous en repos comme elle.\nQue le fil des rois se démêle,\nTournez vos fuseaux, et riez.\nVoyez Bude, votre voisine ;\nVoyez Dristra la sarrasine !\nQue dirait l'Etna si Messine\nFaisait tout ce bruit à ses pieds ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "\" Semlin est la plus querelleuse :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Elle a toujours les premiers torts.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 81,
                    "line_text": "Croyez-vous que mon eau houleuse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 82,
                    "line_text": "Suivant sa pente rocailleuse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 83,
                    "line_text": "N'ait rien à faire entre ses bords",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 84,
                    "line_text": "Qu'à porter à l'Euxin vos morts ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "\" Semlin est la plus querelleuse :\nElle a toujours les premiers torts.\nCroyez-vous que mon eau houleuse,\nSuivant sa pente rocailleuse,\nN'ait rien à faire entre ses bords\nQu'à porter à l'Euxin vos morts ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 13,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 85,
                    "line_text": "\" Vos mortiers ont tant de fumée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 86,
                    "line_text": "Qu'il fait nuit dans ma grotte aimée,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 87,
                    "line_text": "D'éclats d'obus toujours semée !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 88,
                    "line_text": "Du jour j'ai perdu le tableau ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 89,
                    "line_text": "Le soir, la vapeur de leur bouche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 90,
                    "line_text": "Me couvre d'une ombre farouche,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
